'From Squeak3.1alpha of 28 February 2001 [latest update: #4027] on 16 May 2001 at 4:57:14 pm'!"Change Set:		RemoveWin32SupportDate:			16 May 2001Author:			Andreas RaabRemove the Win32 accelerator support code - it's going to be bundled with the standard windows support code so there's no point in leaving it in the image."!!B3DAcceleratorPlugin class methodsFor: 'translation' stamp: 'ar 5/16/2001 16:57'!translateOn: cg inlining: inlineFlag to: fullName local: localFlag	| files path |	super translateOn: cg inlining: inlineFlag to: fullName local: localFlag.	files _ #(		(sqOpenGLRendererHeaderFile 'sqOpenGLRenderer.h')		(sqOpenGLRendererFile 'sqOpenGLRenderer.c')	).	(Smalltalk platformName = 'Mac OS') ifTrue:[		files _ files, #(			(sqMacOpenGLHeaderFile 'sqMacOpenGL.h')			(sqMacOpenGLFile 'sqMacOpenGL.c')			(sqMacOpenGLInfoFile 'sqMacOpenGLInfo')		).	].	path _ (FileDirectory dirPathFor: fullName), FileDirectory slash.	files do:[:spec|		self storeString: (self perform: spec first) onFileNamed: path, spec last.	].! !B3DAcceleratorPlugin class removeSelector: #sqWin32D3DFile!B3DAcceleratorPlugin class removeSelector: #sqWin32OpenGLFile!B3DAcceleratorPlugin class removeSelector: #sqWin32OpenGLHeaderFile!